<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/user/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/user> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Interacts with a regulated process without any blockchain knowledge. No wallet, no ADA, no keys. Receives a signing capability (device or app), performs the regulated action (tap, scan, click), and passes the baton to the next actor. From the user's perspective: receive, use, pass on. The cryptography is invisible." .
