<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/smart-contract/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/schema/#the-on-chain-architecture"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/smart-contract/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Schema section" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/smart-contract/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/smart-contract> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The regulation in executable form. Published by the regulator as a Plutus validator. Governs the operator's trie and reads both the identity trie and regulation trie as reference inputs. Validates every state transition: actor key in identity trie, actor qualified in regulation trie, beacon genuine, commitment exists, slot in window, signatures valid, leaf update matches payload, root hash consistent." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/smart-contract> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#schema> .
