<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/signing-function/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/schema/#the-signing-function"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/signing-function/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Schema section" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/signing-function/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/signing-function> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "An off-chain opaque capability that produces signatures when invoked without exposing the private key. Lives on hardware (SE050), phone enclave, server endpoint, TEE, or ZK circuit. Only its public key and signatures appear on-chain. All substrates present the same interface to the validator." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/signing-function> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#schema> .
