<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution/link/0> .
