<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Pattern docs" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Incentivizes third-party data collection. Reporters accumulate rewards in a monotonically increasing counter stored in the MPT alongside item data. Each valid reading adds to the reporter's accumulated total. Withdrawal is a separate transaction. The invariant is formally proved: rewards never decrease." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/reward-distribution> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#protocols> .
