<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/physical-mode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#concept> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/physical-mode> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/schema/#what-the-operator-does"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Schema section" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Participates in the regulated market. Manages a process trie containing items or processes under their responsibility. A transparent pipe: chooses when to batch, but not what goes in. Mints signing functions, creates commitments, verifies off-chain claims against leaf data, collects double-signed payloads, submits transactions, and pays all fees." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#schema> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Operator" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "operator" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#party> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/operator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/patterns/#mpt-per-operator"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Pattern docs" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The primary storage pattern. One UTxO per operator, items as leaves. Cost scales with operators (hundreds) not items (millions). The operator is the sole writer — no contention by design. A manufacturer updating 10,000 batteries or a controller recording 10,000 consent events pays for one root hash update, not 10,000 individual transactions." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#protocols> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "MPT-per-Operator" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "mpt-per-operator" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#protocol> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/mpt-per-operator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/patterns/#lifecycle-state-machine"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Pattern docs" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Status is a field in the MPT leaf. Transitions are validated on-chain with the invariant that no backward transitions occur unless explicitly allowed. Each transition may change the responsible operator. For the Battery Regulation: Virgin to Active to Repurposed to Recycled. For GDPR consent: None to Given to Withdrawn." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#protocols> .
