<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/lifecycle-state-machine> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#protocol> .
