<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-51-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 51-59" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Independent public authority monitoring GDPR application (Art 51). Maps to the regulator role — maintains the regulation trie with controller standing and certification status. Has investigative, corrective, and advisory powers (Art 58). 27+ national DPAs with EDPB for cross-border consistency. Lead authority mechanism (Art 56) for cross-border processing." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
