<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-supervisory-authority" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-supervisory-authority> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
