<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 15-22" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-12-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 12" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Data subjects may exercise rights of access (Art 15), rectification (Art 16), erasure (Art 17), restriction (Art 18), portability (Art 20), and objection (Art 21). Controller must respond within one month (Art 12(3)), extendable to three months for complex requests. On-chain: commitment-then-submit with slot-bounded window. Timeout without submission is provable non-compliance." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Subject Rights (1 month)" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-rights-requests" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-rights-requests> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-28-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 28" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Processes personal data on behalf of the controller (Art 4(8)). A secondary operator maintaining their own compliance trie, constrained by the controller's documented instructions. The Art 28 processing agreement is a static leaf in both tries. Sub-processors create multi-level trie references — a chain of accountability." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Processor" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-processor" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-30-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 30" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Controllers must maintain records of processing activities: purposes, data categories, recipients, transfers, retention periods, security measures. On-chain: leaves in the controller's trie, all stored as hashes. The SA queries via reference input. On audit, the controller produces pre-images. Hash match proves authenticity and timestamp." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Processing Records (Art 30)" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-processing-records" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-processing-records> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
