<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/1> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://www.enforcementtracker.com/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Enforcement Tracker" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-83-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 83" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Two-tier penalty system. Tier 1: up to 10M EUR or 2% global turnover for controller/processor obligation breaches. Tier 2: up to 20M EUR or 4% global turnover for violations of processing principles, data subject rights, and cross-border transfer rules (Art 83). Plus right to compensation (Art 82) and criminal penalties (Art 84). The strongest liveness incentive of any regulation analysed." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Fines" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-fines" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-fines> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
