<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-35-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 35" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Mandatory when processing is likely to result in high risk (Art 35). Must assess necessity, proportionality, risks, and mitigating measures. On-chain: attestation hash with timestamp proving when the DPIA was conducted relative to processing start. If the SA requires prior consultation (Art 36), the consultation record is also anchored." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Protection Impact Assessment" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-dpia" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-dpia> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
