<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Chapter III" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-4-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 4(1)" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Any identified or identifiable natural person. Maps to the user role — exercises rights via signing function in process mode. No wallet needed. Interacts through the controller's portal. The signing function is the authenticated session. Has extensive rights (access, rectification, erasure, portability, objection) that create commitment-then-submit obligations for the controller." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Subject" .
