<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-data-subject> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-44-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 44-49" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Any transfer to a third country requires safeguards: adequacy decisions (Art 45), Standard Contractual Clauses (Art 46), Binding Corporate Rules (Art 47), or derogations (Art 49). On-chain: hash of the transfer safeguard referenced in the controller's trie. Critical nuance: the on-chain hashes themselves do not constitute a cross-border transfer because they are not personal data." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-cross-border> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Cross-Border Transfers" .
