<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 24" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-4-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 4" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The natural or legal person that determines the purposes and means of processing personal data (Art 4(7)). Maps to the operator role in the schema — maintains their own compliance trie governed by the SA's smart contract. Bears primary accountability. Must demonstrate compliance via the accountability principle (Art 5(2)). Joint controllers (Art 26) may share or cross-reference tries." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Data Controller" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-controller" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-controller> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
