<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-7-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 7" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Freely given, specific, informed, and unambiguous indication of the data subject's wishes (Art 4(11)). On-chain representation: lifecycle state machine (None to Given to Withdrawn). Each transition is a leaf update with timestamped hash. The controller must demonstrate consent existed (Art 7(1)). Withdrawal must be as easy as giving (Art 7(3)) — maps to a single leaf update." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Consent" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-consent" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#gdpr-element> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-consent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://gdpr-info.eu/art-42-gdpr/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 42" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Voluntary data protection certification mechanisms, valid for maximum three years, renewable. Issued by accredited certification bodies or by the SA. On-chain: token with enforced expiry minted by an authorised party in the regulation trie. Expired or revoked tokens cannot be referenced in new compliance submissions. Adherence demonstrates compliance (Art 24(3))." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#gdpr> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Certification (Art 42)" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-certification> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "gdpr-certification" .
