<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-breach-notification/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "GDPR Art 34" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr-breach-notification/link/1> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
