<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "GDPR (EU 2016/679) analysed through the framework. The key reframing: personal data never touches the chain — only compliance evidence (consent hashes, breach notification timestamps, rights-request response proofs). Pure process mode. All five constraints pass. Strongest penalties of any regulation analysed (up to 4% global turnover). Flagship protocol: 72-hour breach notification via commitment-then-submit." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/gdpr> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#cases> .
