<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/cross-operator-handoff/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Pattern docs" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/cross-operator-handoff/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/cross-operator-handoff> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "Transfers responsibility between parties. Old leaf becomes read-only in the originating trie. New leaf is created in the receiving operator's trie with a back-link to the original root, preserving full provenance. Used in Battery Regulation for repurposing and in GDPR for data portability between controllers." .
