<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#externalLink> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol/link/0> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol/link/0> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#url> "https://lambdasistemi.github.io/cardano-for-regulators/framework/patterns/#beacon-gated-attestation"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Pattern docs" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol/link/0> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#ExternalLink> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The regulator requires that user contributions can only be validated if the operator's current standing is disclosed. The operator samples their standing from the regulation trie and relays it to the user. The user signs their data together with this disclosure. The smart contract enforces that the standing was current at submission time. The operator cannot filter or suppress the regulator's assessment." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#protocols> .
