<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#nodeId> "beacon-protocol" .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/isPartOf> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/kinds#protocol> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon-protocol> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#Node> .
