<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#description> "The regulator's policy carrier. Forces the operator to sample their standing and the applicable data policy from the regulation trie before collecting user attestations. Carries two things: standing (the regulator's assessment of the operator) and data policy (who may receive the data — recipient keys per context). The user encrypts their contribution for the beacon's recipients and signs over the beacon. Expires to prevent stale reputation and stale disclosure authorization." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/cardano-for-regulators/rdf/node/beacon> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#schema> .
